  "description": "<p><em><strong>Reachfield Security (Grade “A” agency) specialises in supplying security manpower to Schools, Factories, Shopping Centres, Museums, libraries, etc.</strong></em></p><p><strong>[Office Building]</strong></p><p><em><strong>Permanent Day Senior Security Officer</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Salary: up to $$3430 gross a month </strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Location: Tampines & Raffles Place</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Permanent Day & Night Security Officer</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Salary: up to $3130 gross a month </strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Location: Buona Vista </strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Permanent Day Security Officer cum Concierge</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Salary: up to $3130 gross a month </strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Location: Marina Bay</strong></em></p><p><strong>[School]</strong></p><p><em><strong>Permanent Day Security Officer - School (5.5 days, Sunday Off)</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Salary: up to $3120 gross a month </strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Location: Serangoon North</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Permanent Day Security Officer - School (5.5 days, Sunday Off)</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Salary: up to $3120 gross a month </strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Location: Tiong Bahru</strong></em><br /></p><p>////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br /></p><p>1. Works in a school/ office building environment.</p><p>2. Good customer service skills; able to communicate with people of all levels.</p><p>3. 12hrs-shift (Fixed shift, no need to rotate)</p><p>4. PC knowledge required.</p><p>5. Job duties include traffic control, issue visitors/ contractor passes, patrolling, protecting clients’ premises and access control, etc.</p><p>6. Possess valid security license, completed WSQ RTT.</p><p>Walk-in for interviews - (Mon to Fri, 9am to 5pm) </p><p>10 Anson Road #26-09</p><p>International Plaza, Singapore 079903</p><p>(Tanjong Pagar MRT)</p><p><strong>For more information, please call the office at 6324 0648 / 9139 3211 (Amelia) </strong></p><p>You may fill in the application form online thru below link.</p><p>https://rss.armfort.com/direct... </p><p>Do let us know once you submit the application online</p>",
